description: Stickin’ the Landing is a relaxing puzzle game where you use stickers and their gravitational properties to guide a spaceship adrift around outlandish worlds until you reach your destination. Travel through the home’s nooks and crannies and discover everything this marvelous universe has to offer!
name: Stickin' the Landing
intro: Puzzles, Stickers and a universe to explore! The gravity will be your guide in this unique adventure!
